cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.COM

This paper discusses the challenges and opportunities of mobile and wireless networks, and proposes solutions using software-defined networking and network virtualization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also touches upon security (cs.CR), system engineering (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and communication (cs.COM) aspects, which are relevant to the topic.
